channel.title: Need verry fast and probobly easy help
channel.description:
Hello every one i have downloded "darkscape" but when i try to start it on "runserver" it nnot work it just come up: [img]http://img149.imageshack.us/img149/7241/untitledxt7.png[/img]

plz need fast help here!

item.title: Need verry fast and probobly easy help
item.dc:creator: @oh_yeah oh yeah
item.description:
@oh_yeah wrote:

just make sure u put everyhing in like it is said here:

right click the compile file and delete everything it says and put in

@echo off
title (yourservernamehere)
“C:Program FilesJavajdk1.5.0_09injavac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:Program FilesJavajdk1.5.0_09injava.exe” server
pause

then right click the runserver…delete everything, put in

@echo off
title (yourservernamehere)
java -Xmx1024m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar serve

at the “(yourservernamehere)” u put in the name of ur server like: ‘darknessscape’
